QuestData.Title: To the Withering
QuestData.Description: According to Magatha, she'll meet you just outside of the Twilight Withering to the east.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Magatha Grimtotem at the Twilight Withering in Thousand Needles.
QuestData.RewardText: It took you long enough. Do you think that we are playing games here?
